{"tid":1970643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑爆假核爆，無人推","createTime":"2020-04-13T09:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T09:51:57.000Z","uid":229185,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fddce9cfeceb4ae867f3cc5e74d4065d7aecf050","tid":1970643,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6Y59w5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6Y59w5.jpg&h=b524b2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國特里爾市，馬克思在此出生。為慶祝馬克思誕辰二百周年，中國向此城送出馬克思銅像。<br />\n<br />\n今日德國市民為中國製造的馬克思銅像戴上「冠狀病毒」王冠，披上病毒紅旗，以示瘟神始祖之意。<br />\n<br />\n如此辱華，實令人憤慨。看見德國人此種族主義的行為，還不即刻將平治汽車拖出砸毀、以護黨國初心的，還算是中國人嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GzMGHSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzMGHSC.jpg&h=c17eb6d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6925e6865f315c01fb308989a7057f9d1ce5a2db","tid":1970643,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T09:51:57.000Z","msg":"ok"}]}